According to our [supported platforms|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Supported+Platforms] we don't support Oracle 10G any longer. Confusingly although, customers are to set up their instance using the parameters set out [here|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Connecting+JIRA+to+Oracle].

Namely this attribute in the dbconfig.xml file:
{code}
  <database-type>oracle10g</database-type>
{code}

