{code}
     Loading entityengine.xml from                 : file:/home/rpillai/atlassian/jiralive/atlassian-jira/WEB-INF/classes/entityengine.xml
     Entity model field type name                  : oracle10g
     Entity model schema name                      : 
     Database Version                              : Oracle - Oracle Database 11g Express Edition Release 11.2.0.2.0 - 64bit Beta
     Database Driver                               : Oracle JDBC driver - 11.2.0.2.0
     Database URL                                  : jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521:XE
     Database JDBC config                          : oracle10g jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521:XE
{code}

It would be less confusing if the JDBC driver could output that it was configured for an 11g database, and not a 10g database.

